  <li>Preheat the oven to 220°C.</li>
  <li>Prepare the pizza bases by spreading the crème fraîche over the base.</li>
  <li>Sprinkle with the Gruyère and top with the onions, salami (or smoked salmon) and olives (or capers).</li>
  <li>Finally, top with a sprinkling of pizza cheese.</li>
  <li>Bake in the hot oven for 10 minutes.</li>
  <li>Serve when golden.</li>
